1. agar kbhi hume jarurat ho  boolean function ki to vo true false return krega but
last me main function par aake if case m jarur dalo 
bhul jate ho tum baar baar (check Search in 2D matrix II for reference purpose )

2. agar lower bound and upper bound in 2D vmatrix use karo to dyan do agr koi answer na de to vo (ans=n) 
deta h to uska case main function pr handle krna jaruri hai.

3. hashing same hi hoti h 1D and 2D me bas do loop lag jate h
 in hashset please dont first add element to hashset and then check for condition
 instead do check whether element present or not if not use else for add and yes use if for that or vice versa just get the context clear 

 4. agar Constraints:
1 <= arr.size() <= 10^5 ho to nested loop use nhi krenge vo tle dega pakka 